  "title": "Senior Visual Merchandiser",
  "description": "<p>Job Description</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Conceptualize and implement attractive, creative and innovative store displays according to Company’s plans and guidelines</li>\n  <li>Work closely with franchise partners for in-store and window display, review VM reports and provide comments accordingly</li>\n  <li>Optimizes and maintains the use of visual assets such as fixtures, props and marketing; ensures all marketing and creative layer is current</li>\n  <li>Efficient undertaking of monthly VM related administration procedures such as budgeting, prop sourcing and VM store visit report</li>\n  <li>Raising quotations</li>\n  <li>Support when necessary on permanent and temporary projects</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Job Requirments</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Familiar with the visual merchandise industry (A plus to have at least 2 years relevant working experience)</li>\n  <li>Diploma / Degree in Visual Merchandising, Fashion Merchandising, Exhibition Design, Visual Communications or similar</li>\n  <li>Great at communicating visually and verbally</li>\n  <li>Excellent at time management and are comfortable with working in a fast-paced environment</li>\n  <li>Motivated, organized and detail-oriented; able to work independently</li>\n  <li>Mature, organized and able to work under pressure</li>\n</ul>",
