    "description": "<p>Vision Display Pte Ltd was incorporated on 17 December 2013.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Vision Display is one of the all-in production houses in Singapore, with contracts all throughout South-East Asia.&nbsp;</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>We specialize in digital printing in any format and carpentry production as well as signage manufacturing. We have the expertise, manpower and the necessary infrastructure to carry out popup stores and events installation on-site and we offer digital printing, finishing, ready to use advertising solutions systems such as large-format print advertising (banners, mesh and posters), billboards, flags, banners, textile and many others.</p>",
